readme:
Boogie for Atom
================

Syntax highlighting for Microsoft's Boogie verification language to be used with the Atom text editor.

Boogie is an open-source project and can be found in CodePlex:

* [Boogie @ CodePlex][1]

[1]: https://boogie.codeplex.com
